title: Criminal | Cast Announcement | Netflix
excerpt: Step into the interrogation room and discover 12 unique crime stories from the UK, France, Germany and Spain. Coming this Fall. Only on Netflix. SUBSCRIBE: h...
description: David Tennant, Hayley Atwell y Nicholas Pinnock serán los protagonistas de Criminal, un drama que se enfocará en el intenso conflicto mental entre un policía y un sospechoso que está siendo interrogado, todos los capítulos ocurrirán exclusivamente en una sala de interrogatorio.Serán 12 episodios de 45 minutos cada uno, se desarrollarán en Francia, España, Alemania e Inglaterra, en cada país se producirán 3 episodios en el lenguaje local y escrito y dirigido por talento de cada país.

summary:
The greatest thing about Good Omens is that,
If someone told you that a demon and an angel had to work together to stop the end...
body:
The greatest thing about Good Omens is that,

If someone told you that a demon and an angel had to work together to stop the end of the world, one after persuasion and mostly because he really enjoyed human-created pleasures (food, books…) and the other one because he just loved humans (and also his eternal romantic interest frenemy), you would think that the first one was the demon and the other the ever-loving angel.

And yet
